34:01.493 --> 34:03.367
- You like that cover?
- I like it, it's beautiful.

34:05.240 --> 34:07.531
I thank Virgilio
for this book.

34:07.532 --> 34:10.237
He gave me a lesson
in literature and editing.

34:10.550 --> 34:12.735
... my brothers Juan
and Nicholas are writers too.

34:12.737 --> 34:13.985
Oh, come on.

34:14.089 --> 34:16.483
Pepe, we've got the Bronte
sisters in the back-seat.

34:16.483 --> 34:17.628
Look at them.

34:25.123 --> 34:28.351
Lezama is a Catholic;
Virgilio is an atheist.

34:29.288 --> 34:31.369
