he writes everything by hand.

34:35.221 --> 34:37.614
Something you
wouldn't understand

34:37.617 --> 34:39.906
It's called
intellectual honesty.

34:40.842 --> 34:42.404
I don't understand!

34:42.405 --> 34:45.007
Well, if you took the time
to actually read their books,

34:45.007 --> 34:47.297
