36:09.119 --> 36:10.889
What's your name?

36:12.034 --> 36:13.492
My name?

36:14.845 --> 36:16.719
Franz Kafka.

36:16.719 --> 36:18.801
Franz Kafka.

36:18.801 --> 36:20.362
