wonderful things

38:10.916 --> 38:13.116
that I enjoyed
in the 60's:

38:13.535 --> 38:18.040
my typewriter, at which I sat
like a dedicated performer

38:18.040 --> 38:19.716
sitting at his piano;

38:20.554 --> 38:22.649
the youth of those days,

38:22.649 --> 38:25.268
when everyone was ready
to break free;

38:25.792 --> 38:29.877
and lastly, the full discovery
of the sea.

