he's gay,

40:22.387 --> 40:24.690
there's no limit
to his sexual voracity,

40:24.691 --> 40:27.519
therefore he's constantly
being arrested.

40:27.520 --> 40:29.823
The system has created
a permanent collar

40:29.823 --> 40:31.080
around his neck,

40:31.080 --> 40:32.337
so they can
hook him up

40:32.337 --> 40:33.909
and take him to
a rehabilitation camp

40:33.909 --> 40:35.375
like a Valparaíso.

40:35.585 --> 40:37.889
Two is the common gay.

40:37.890 --> 40:40.404
He's made his commitments
with other gays,

40:40.405 --> 40:42.603
has a job, film clubs,

40:42.603 --> 40:44.908
likes to sip tea
with his friends,

40:44.909 --> 40:46.375
