47:35.571 --> 47:37.869
I am aware of my errors.

47:42.152 --> 47:44.137
that are unpardonable,

47:45.286 --> 47:48.420
errors that demand
to be severely punished.

47:49.987 --> 47:53.434
But I must confess
that I see before me

47:53.435 --> 47:55.105
in this room,

47:55.210 --> 47:58.866
the faces of many comrades
who like me,

47:58.867 --> 48:01.060
have lost their way,

48:01.061 --> 48:04.925
whose ideology has waivered,

48:04.926 --> 48:07.745
who have committed
similar errors...

48:07.746 --> 48:15.998
errors that also demand
to be severely punished.

49:05.618 --> 49:08.334
I'm sorry.
I'm late.

49:08.648 --> 49:11.155
We got a call about
an hour ago.

49:11.156 --> 49:13.244
They said they would be
at the Hotel Nacional

49:13.245 --> 49:15.542
