01:07:49.056 --> 01:07:51.351
Adriano Faustino Sotolongo.

01:07:53.646 --> 01:07:55.733
When did you get
that name, Reinaldo?

01:07:55.734 --> 01:07:58.341
You are Reinaldo Arenas,
aren't you?

01:08:08.252 --> 01:08:09.713
Buen trabajo.

01:08:11.904 --> 01:08:13.677
Officer: Mira, encontramos
este paquete.

01:08:50.296 --> 01:08:51.950
Este es Reinaldo Arenas,

01:08:51.950 --> 01:08:54.015
un pájaro que agarramos
ahí en el parque.

01:08:57.631 --> 01:09:00.006
Dale! Dale!

01:09:00.006 --> 01:09:02.073
Dale, coño!
Dale!

01:09:03.002 --> 01:09:04.863
Ya vas a ver
lo que es bueno.

01:09:04.863 --> 01:09:07.238
Vas a ver lo que es bueno
ahí adentro.

01:09:23.767 --> 01:09:27.383
I arrived at El Morro not
as a political prisoner

01:09:27.383 --> 01:09:28.519
or writer,

01:09:28.519 --> 01:09:32.548
but with an infamous
reputation as a rapist,

01:09:32.549 --> 01:09:35.234
a murderer,
and a CIA agent.

01:09:41.122 --> 01:09:43.188
a supernatural air
of nonchalance

01:09:43.189 --> 01:09:46.287
and gave me an aura
of danger and respectability

01:09:46.287 --> 01:09:48.767
among the real murderers,

01:09:48.768 --> 01:09:50.316
real rapists,

01:09:50.317 --> 01:09:52.589
and common criminals
who would kill each other

01:09:52.590 --> 01:09:53.828
for the slightest reason.

01:10:13.766 --> 01:10:16.969
Skies lit by bolts
of lightning

01:10:16.969 --> 01:10:19.138
were replaced
by electric lights

01:10:19.139 --> 01:10:21.824
that blinked on and off
with regularity,

01:10:21.824 --> 01:10:25.130
killing the possibility
or chance that I might dream

01:10:25.130 --> 01:10:26.782
or forget where I was.

01:10:28.642 --> 01:10:30.811
I thought here
I could go unnoticed.

01:10:30.811 --> 01:10:34.633
But prisoners are those
beings that know everything,

01:10:34.633 --> 01:10:37.009
especially about
other prisoners.

01:10:48.373 --> 01:10:51.162
Soon they knew,
maybe from the guards,

01:10:51.163 --> 01:10:54.468
or the warden himself,
or a killer named Torre,

01:10:54.468 --> 01:10:56.017
that I was a writer.

01:10:56.018 --> 01:10:59.943
Say, you think you could
write a letter for me?

01:10:59.944 --> 01:11:00.976
What?

01:11:01.079 --> 01:11:02.216
Not for nothing,

01:11:03.352 --> 01:11:05.315
I give you two cigarettes.

01:11:05.728 --> 01:11:07.071
Carlota--

01:11:07.072 --> 01:11:11.513
tell her that I miss
her so much.

01:11:11.514 --> 01:11:13.062
Your words or mine?

01:11:15.438 --> 01:11:17.918
I'm sorry.

01:11:28.455 --> 01:11:31.967
My fame as "The Writer"
spread all over the prison.

01:11:33.103 --> 01:11:34.240
María...

01:11:34.240 --> 01:11:37.959
From the 17 cells of El Morro,

01:11:37.960 --> 01:11:40.748
and for those who couldn't
see me directly,

01:11:40.748 --> 01:11:44.260
petitions came in the form
of hundreds of balls of soap,

01:11:44.260 --> 01:11:46.016
tied to long strings,

01:11:46.017 --> 01:11:48.805
that the prisoners
could pass on to my cell.

01:11:49.529 --> 01:11:51.285
It was called "The Mail. "

01:11:52.524 --> 01:11:54.384
I never wrote so much.

01:11:55.727 --> 01:11:59.032
I accumulated a small
fortune of cigarettes

01:11:59.032 --> 01:12:02.132
that provided me with
enough paper and pencils

01:12:02.133 --> 01:12:03.475
for my own novel,

01:12:03.578 --> 01:12:05.127
which I wrote in the middle,

01:12:05.127 --> 01:12:07.917
of all the screaming
and crying.

01:12:07.918 --> 01:12:11.739
Cubans are defined by noise,
it's their nature.

01:12:11.740 --> 01:12:13.908
They need to bother others.

01:12:13.909 --> 01:12:17.214
They can neither enjoy,
nor suffer in silence.

01:12:22.276 --> 01:12:24.342
Even the sun was rationed,

01:12:24.343 --> 01:12:26.924
but once a month
the gay inmates

01:12:26.925 --> 01:12:29.094
turned El Morro
into a nightclub.

01:12:30.230 --> 01:12:32.400
Leonardo da Vinci
was homosexual,

01:12:32.401 --> 01:12:37.255
so was Michelangelo,
Socrates, Shakespeare,

01:12:37.256 --> 01:12:39.321
and almost every other
figure that has formed

01:12:39.321 --> 01:12:41.903
what we have come
to understand as beauty.

01:12:41.903 --> 01:12:45.622
Bon Bon, the hearthrob
of El Morro,

01:12:45.623 --> 01:12:47.379
was no different.

01:12:47.380 --> 01:12:50.478
She was so glamorous,
that when she walked by,

01:12:50.478 --> 01:12:53.577
she made everybody feel
like they were in the movies.

01:12:55.643 --> 01:12:58.639
