for another quality.

01:12:58.640 --> 01:13:01.428
He was one
of those transporters,

01:13:01.429 --> 01:13:03.700
who by the grace
of countless activity,

01:13:03.702 --> 01:13:06.696
could carry unfathomable
quantities in the deepness

01:13:06.697 --> 01:13:11.448
of his rectum, even if given
a thorough ass check.

01:13:28.287 --> 01:13:29.216
