01:13:30.663 --> 01:13:33.245
I heard that you can get
things in and out of here.

01:13:35.725 --> 01:13:38.824
Could you carry
a package for me?

01:13:38.825 --> 01:13:40.167
Of course,
he denied it.

01:13:42.543 --> 01:13:45.229
